bilingual.source: The door is next to the desk.
The desk is next to the door.
The window is between the bed and the desk.
He does his homework at the desk.

list.abstract: desk（英[desk]，美[desk]），英语单词，词性是名词，释义为书桌、登记处、部等。例句：She hoicked her bag on to the desk.（她使劲把包拉到书桌上。） desk的复数是desks。短语搭配有front desk（前台）、writing desk（书桌）、desk job（文职工作）等。近义词为bureau、Information Counter。

yingyinNormal.en: You said I could buy a desk. This isn't a desk. This is a brobdingnagian monstrosity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是你说我可以买张书桌的。这东西压根不是书桌，这是个...硕大无朋的怪物。

yingyinNormal.en: Help me move my desk. No. Yes. No. Yes. No. It's too Brobdingnagian.
yingyinNormal.zh: 帮我搬一下我的书桌。不。搬。不。搬。不，这也过于硕大无朋了。

yingyinNormal.en: Is that the American idiom for giant, big-ass desk? It's actually British.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是美国俗语里面对"巨大的书桌"的叫法吗？其实是英式英语的说法。

yingyinNormal.en: And we could have a roll top desk with little comment cards on them so people could say how much they loved staying here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再摆张书桌放上留言卡，让客人表达他们的开心。

yingyinNormal.en: All right. This is my desk. These are my books. This is my door. Please close it behind you. Good-bye.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，这是我的书桌，这些是我的书，这是我的门，出去，请随手关门，再见。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you want to see my desk now?
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在你想看看我的办公桌吗？

yingyinNormal.en: No. The desk. Left-hand drawer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在写字台。左手边的抽屉。

yingyinNormal.en: On with the tour. Next up is Mrs. Cat's desk.
yingyinNormal.zh: 继续我们的参观，下一站是猫女士的办公桌。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, mom. What you doing? I'm looking at this desk.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈妈，你干嘛呢？我在看这张桌子。

yingyinNormal.en: You're being unreasonable. Why can't I have a desk?!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你开始蛮横无理了，为什么我就不能有张桌子？！

yingyinNormal.en: There's Neosporin and Band Aids in my top desk drawer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 上面抽屉里有Neosporin抗生素药膏和邦迪。

yingyinNormal.en: Hello? Miss Jones, please. Samantha. It's the front desk.
yingyinNormal.zh: 喂，请转琼斯小姐。萨曼莎，前台打来的。

yingyinNormal.en: Like this desk, for instance. It could be something special.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就像这张桌子，它可以变得很特别。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, what if he buys his own desk? Yeah, what if I buy my own desk?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，那他出钱买自己的桌子呢？是啊，要是我买我自己的桌子呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Do you want to see my desk now? Yes, please. This is Daddy Pig's desk.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在你想看看我的办公桌吗？是的，我想。这是猪爸爸的办公桌。

yingyinNormal.en: Why don't you just eat in your desk chair? Why don't I just eat in my desk chair? Here we go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么不坐在办公椅那吃？我怎么不坐在办公椅那吃？开始了。

yingyinNormal.en: That is my desk chair. That is where I work. I don't eat in my desk chair and I don't work in my spot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是我的办公椅，是我工作的地方，我不在办公椅那吃饭，也不在专座上工作。

yingyinNormal.en: Edith! What did you put on my desk? A mud pie.
yingyinNormal.zh: 伊迪丝！你把什么放我桌上了？泥巴派

yingyinNormal.en: Good, come on back in, and I'll assign you a desk.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很好，明天过来，我给你安排张桌子。太好了。

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon. All right, all right. He can buy his own desk.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿。好了，好了，他可以买他自己的桌子了。

examination_example.sentence: But can you be sure you've noted every snack bar in your car, or every handful of nuts at your <highlight>desk</highlight>?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是你能确定你记下了车里的每一个小吃店，或者你办公桌上的每一把坚果吗？

examination_example.sentence: They've had to call the help <highlight>desk</highlight> for the same issue.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们不得不为同样的问题打电话给服务台。

examination_example.sentence: As I was considering all this, a press release from a respected research firm crossed my <highlight>desk</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 就在我考虑这一切的时候，一份来自一家受人尊敬的研究公司的新闻稿掠过我的办公桌。

direction_info.description:

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: I would go to the office, sit at my <highlight>desk</highlight> and repeat the same work five days a week 9 to 5.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我会去办公室，坐在办公桌前，每周五天，朝九晚五地重复同样的工作。

examination_example.sentence: Hundreds of people have formed impressions of you through that little device (装置) on your <highlight>desk</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 数以百计的人通过你桌上的那个小装置对你形成了印象。

examination_example.sentence: The woman sitting at the <highlight>desk</highlight>, seeing my madness, sympathetically jumped up.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 坐在桌旁的女人看到我的疯狂，同情地跳了起来。

examination_example.sentence: The lockers are located in Building 1 near the Information <highlight>Desk</highlight> and in Building 3.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 储物柜位于1号楼服务台附近和3号楼。

examination_example.sentence: Pushchairs and wheelchairs are available to rent at the Information <highlight>Desk</highlight> and Denny Way entrance.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在问询处和丹尼路入口处有折叠式婴儿车和轮椅可供租用。

examination_example.sentence: When I arrived at the check-in <highlight>desk</highlight> at Providence, the lady on the <highlight>desk</highlight> said: "Well, I'm really sorry."
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当我到达普罗维登斯的登记处时，服务台的女士说：“嗯，我真的很抱歉。”
